PROJECT 4: RECOMMENDATION SYSTEM
Title

Movie Recommendation System Using C

Objective

To recommend movies based on user-selected genres.

Description

Recommendation systems are widely used in online platforms. This project recommends movies according to user preferences.

Algorithm
Display movie categories.
Accept user choice.
Match choice with recommendations.
Display suggested movies.
End program.
Source Code
#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
    int choice;

    printf("===== MOVIE RECOMMENDATION SYSTEM =====\n");

    printf("1. Action\n");
    printf("2. Comedy\n");
    printf("3. Horror\n");

    printf("Enter Choice: ");
    scanf("%d",&choice);

    switch(choice)
    {
        case 1:
            printf("\nRecommended Movies:\n");
            printf("Avengers\n");
            printf("Batman\n");
            break;

        case 2:
            printf("\nRecommended Movies:\n");
            printf("Mr Bean\n");
            printf("Home Alone\n");
            break;

        case 3:
            printf("\nRecommended Movies:\n");
            printf("Conjuring\n");
            printf("Insidious\n");
            break;

        default:
            printf("Invalid Choice\n");
    }

    return 0;
}
